                    "effect": "You swing the dagger in a wide arc, causing a horizontal swipe of blood- red energy to sweep out in a 30-foot cone. All living creatures in the area take 15d6 slashing damage (DC 34 basic Reflex save), plus 1d6 persistent bleed damage on a failed save.",
